enhanced_by.reason: Both methods require similar parameters such as 'projectId' or 'productId' and 'amount', which can be reused for setting up test cases.
The 'lockedProductList' method provides a list of locked products, which can be used to set up the initial state for testing 'subscribeLockedProduct'.
The 'lockedSubscriptionRecord' method retrieves records of locked subscriptions, which can be used to verify the successful subscription in 'subscribeLockedProduct'.
The 'lockedProductPosition' method can be used to verify the state of the locked product position after a subscription, providing additional assertions for 'subscribeLockedProduct'.
